msgid ""
"Before you can use the ARIN TAL, you need to agree to the ARIN Relying "
"Party Agreement (RPA). You can find it at "
"https://www.arin.net/resources/manage/rpki/rpa.pdf and explicitly agree "
"to it via this option. This explicit agreement is necessary in order to "
"install the ARIN TAL."
