#: ../../source/routinator/manual-page.rst:494
msgid ""
"You can provide a number of addresses and ports to listen on for RTR and "
"HTTP through command line options or their configuration file equivalent."
" Currently, Routinator will only start listening on these ports after an "
"initial validation run has finished."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/routinator/manual-page.rst:499
msgid ""
"It will not listen on any sockets unless explicitly specified. It will "
"still run and periodically update the repository. This might be useful "
"for use with :subcmd:`vrps` mode with the :option:`-n` option."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/routinator/manual-page.rst:505
msgid ""
"If present, Routinator will detach from the terminal after a successful "
"start."
